3.npm설치
$npm install -g npm
Node.js v14.16.1 to /usr/local/bin/node
npm v6.14.12 to /usr/local/bin/npm
Make sure that /usr/local/bin is in your $PATH.

*터미널 조회
$npm -v
$node -v

